    "Choukroun et al. [42] proposed a model with a different self-attention mechanism, more similar to Maziarka et al.",
    "[12], that, trained with their custom data augmentation, outperforms R-MAT in the QM9 task.",
    "Wu et al. [43] proposed Molformer -an architecture that exploits both molecular 3D geometry and its motifs.",
    "Their model surpasses R-MAT in the QM7, BBBP, and BACE tasks.",
    "Atom relation embeddingOur core idea to improve Molecule Self-Attention is to add flexibility in how it processes graph and distance information."
